// BT-2475: Stable announcement event fixture for SystemNavigation
// `announcementsSentBy:` E2E tests. A concrete `Announcement` subclass with a
// keyword constructor (`AnnounceEventA payload:`) so the emitter fixture's
// `announce: (AnnounceEventA payload: 1)` resolves to this class.

Announcement subclass: AnnounceEventA
  field: payload :: Integer = 0
